'''凱文·李·鮑爾森'''（Kevin Lee Poulsen，{{bd|1965年|11月30日|||Poulsen, Kevin}}）為美國的一位{{link-en|數位安全|digital security}}領域的[[新聞從業員|新聞從業員]]，曾是位[[黑客_(计算机安全)|黑帽駭客]]，生於[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加州]][[帕萨迪纳_(加利福尼亚州)|帕薩迪納]]。<ref name="book">{{cite book|last=Gissel|first=Richard|title=Digital Underworld|edition=2005-08-23|publisher=Lulu.com|isbn=1-4116-4423-9|page=222|quote=Kevin Lee Poulsen was born in Pasadena, California in 1965. It was claimed that when he was 17 he used his radio shack TRS-80 to attack Arpanet, the predecessor of the Internet.|language=en}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
=== 黑帽駭客 ===
鮑爾森在網路上匿名為「黑暗但丁」（{{lang|en|Dark Dante}}）<ref name="latimes">{{Cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1993-09-12/magazine/tm-34163_1_kevin-poulsen|accessdate=2015-11-29|title=The Last Hacker : He Called Himself Dark Dante. His Compulsion Led Him to Secret Files and, Eventually, the Bar of Justice|author=Jonathan Littman|date=1993-09-12|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151205044550/http://articles.latimes.com/1993-09-12/magazine/tm-34163_1_kevin-poulsen|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在17歲便用其{{link-en|TRS-80|TRS-80}}電腦駭入[[美國國防部|美國國防部]]的[[ARPANET|高等研究計劃署網路]]，但他並沒有被起訴，隨後成為{{link-en|國際史丹佛學會|SRI International|SRI}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.computerhistory.org/events/bio/Kevin,Poulsen|title=Kevin Poulsen|publisher=[[計算機歷史博物館|計算機歷史博物館]]|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208045232/http://www.computerhistory.org/events/bio/Kevin,Poulsen|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[昇陽電腦|昇陽]]的程式員，負責測試{{link-en|五角電腦|Pentagon (computer)}}的安全性<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nndb.com/people/453/000022387/|title=Kevin Poulsen|publisher={{link-en|著名名稱資料庫|NNDB}}|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202134704/http://www.nndb.com/people/453/000022387/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在其23歲時，因多次駭入[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]的網路並竄改檔案，遭到聯邦調查局的通緝，鮑爾森開始了流亡生涯<ref name="mental">{{Cite web|url=http://mentalfloss.com/article/26767/4-famous-hackers-who-got-caught|title=4 Famous Hackers Who Got Caught|accessdate=2015-11-29|publisher={{link-en|Mental Floss|Mental Floss}}|date=2011-01-03|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208131119/http://mentalfloss.com/article/26767/4-famous-hackers-who-got-caught|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在17個月的流亡過程中，鮑爾森亦多次入侵聯邦調查局的檔案庫作為報復，被聯邦調查局稱作「[[電腦犯罪|電腦犯罪]]界的[[漢尼拔·萊克特|漢尼拔·萊克特]]」<ref name="mental" />；並在一次[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]電臺{{link-en|KIIS-FM|KIIS-FM}}舉辦的活動中，控制了所有該電臺的電話線，使其成為第102個[[Phone-in|叩應]]者而能獲得該電臺提供的大獎[[保时捷|保时捷]][[保時捷944|944 S2]]<ref name="livinginternet">{{cite web|year=2007|url=http://www.livinginternet.com/i/ia_hackers_poulsen.htm|title=Kevin Poulsen|publisher=livinginternet|accessdate=2015-12-28|language=en|archive-date=2016-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160102201118/http://www.livinginternet.com/i/ia_hackers_poulsen.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="FREEDOM">{{cite web |volume=27 |issue=4 |url=http://www.theta.com/goodman/crime.htm |title=A Crime By Any Other Name... |publisher=FREEDOM Magazine |accessdate=2015-11-28 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19990116234531/http://www.theta.com/goodman/crime.htm |archivedate=1999-01-16 }}</ref>。此外當[[國家廣播公司|國家廣播公司]]播出以其為主題的《{{link-en|未解之謎|Unsolved Mysteries}}》節目時，該電視臺的[[免費電話|免費電話專線]]突然不明癱瘓<ref name="livinginternet" /><ref name="itsecurity">{{cite web|year=2007|url=http://www.itsecurity.com/features/top-10-famous-hackers-042407|title=Top 10 Most Famous Hackers of All Time|publisher=itsecurity|accessdate=2015-11-28|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211163323/http://www.itsecurity.com/features/top-10-famous-hackers-042407/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來鮑爾森遭到逮捕，並被判刑五年。其出獄後被禁止使用電腦與網路長達三年，他也是首位被法院判決出獄後禁止使用電腦與網路的美國人{{efn|{{link-en|克里斯·蘭普雷希特|Chris Lamprecht}}在更早前，1995年5月時，亦被判決禁止使用網路，但鮑爾森較之早出獄。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://securelist.com/threats/a-brief-history-of-hacking/|title=A brief history of hacking|publisher=[[卡巴斯基實驗室|卡巴斯基實驗室]]|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208091830/https://securelist.com/threats/a-brief-history-of-hacking/|archive-date=2015-12-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>}}。2004年鮑爾森的{{link-en|假釋官|Probation officer}}允許他在監控之下能使用網路。<ref>{{cite web|year=2004|url=http://archive.wired.com/wired/archive/7.01/poulsen_pr.html|title=Five years behind bars for hacking wasn't punishment enough. Meet the Amazing Modemless Man.|publisher=Wired Magazine|accessdate=2015-11-28|author=凱文·鮑爾森|language=en|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229184852/http://archive.wired.com/wired/archive/7.01/poulsen_pr.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 新聞從業員 ===
鮑爾森出獄後改從事[[新聞從業員|新聞從業]]，並力求與其犯罪往昔切割。鮑爾森在加州的資安研究公司{{link-en|SecurityFocus|SecurityFocus}}擔任一些新聞記者的職位，鮑爾森從2000年開始就已在該公司撰寫過一些駭客、資安相關的新聞。雖然在相關領域的新聞媒體已經飽和的情況下，《SecurityFocus新聞》仍在鮑爾森加入時期內成為科技新聞領域內的著名業者而被[[賽門鐵克|賽門鐵克]]收購；鮑爾森的調查報告也時常被主流媒體提及。2005年他決定離開SecurityFocus以尋找獨立寫作企劃，並在該年6月成為《[[连线|连线]]》雜誌的高級編輯，並在隔年建立自己的部落格「27BStroke6」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blog.wired.com/27BStroke6/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060602160641/http://blog.wired.com/27BStroke6/ |archivedate=2006-06-02 |title=Wired.com |publisher=Blog.wired.com |accessdate=2015-11-29 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，並在後來改名為「Threat Level」<ref>{{cite web|last=Kravets|first=David|url=http://www.wired.com/threatlevel/|title=Threat Level - Privacy, Crime and Security Online|publisher=Wired.com|date=2015-11-29|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2014-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330162246/http://www.wired.com/threatlevel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年10月，鮑爾森透過搜尋與比對[[MySpace|MySpace]]的資料，識別出了744-{位}-潛在兒童[[性罪犯|性罪犯]]，並成功逮捕了其中一位。<ref name="lubrano">{{cite news|url=http://archive.wired.com/science/discoveries/news/2006/10/71948?currentPage=all|title=MySpace Predator Caught by Code|date=2006-10-26|publisher=[[連線_(網站)|Wired News]]|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208071355/http://archive.wired.com/science/discoveries/news/2006/10/71948?currentPage=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== SecureDrop ===
鮑爾森與[[亚伦·斯沃茨|亚伦·斯沃茨]]合力開發了[[開源軟體|開源軟體]]{{link-en|SecureDrop|SecureDrop}}，其為一款讓記者與{{link-en|來源 (新聞)|source (journalism)|-{消息}-來源}}之間{{link-en|加密通訊|secure communication|匿名通訊}}的工具；其原名「DeadDrop」<ref name=kassner2013>{{cite web|url=http://www.techrepublic.com/blog/it-security/aaron-swartz-legacy-lives-on-with-new-yorkers-strongbox-how-it-works/|title=Aaron Swartz legacy lives on with New Yorker's Strongbox: How it works|last1=Kassner|first1=Michael|date=2013-05-20|website=[[TechRepublic|TechRepublic]]|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2013-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729032429/http://www.techrepublic.com/blog/it-security/aaron-swartz-legacy-lives-on-with-new-yorkers-strongbox-how-it-works/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=paulsen2013>{{cite web|url=http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/newsdesk/2013/05/strongbox-and-aaron-swartz.html|title=Strongbox and Aaron Swartz|author=凱文·鮑爾森|date=2013-05-15|website=[[紐約客|紐約客]]|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2013-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605165342/http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/newsdesk/2013/05/strongbox-and-aaron-swartz.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.openfoundry.org/tw/foss-news/9093--aaron-swartz-securedrop|title=自由出版基金會推出 Aaron Swartz 設計的告密工具 SecureDrop|author=謝良奇|accessdate=2015-11-29|date=2013-10-28|language=zh-hant}}{{Dead link|date=2020年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。斯沃茨去世後，2013年5月15日，鮑爾森將SecureDrop首次佈署於《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》<ref name=davidson2013>{{cite web|url=http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/closeread/2013/05/introducing-strongbox-anonymous-document-sharing-tool.html|title=Introducing Strongbox|author={{link-en|Amy Davidson|Amy Davidson (author)}}|date=2013-05-15|website=[[紐約客|紐約客]]|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2013-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629182444/http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/closeread/2013/05/introducing-strongbox-anonymous-document-sharing-tool.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其後又將SecureDrop的開發轉移至[[新聞自由基金會|新聞自由基金會]]旗下，鮑爾森也成為該基金會的科技顧問。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pressfreedomfoundation.org/blog/2013/10/freedom-press-foundation-launches-securedrop|title=Freedom of the Press Foundation Launches SecureDrop, an Open-Source Submission Platform for Whistleblowers|publisher=pressfreedomfoundation.org|date=2013-10-15|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2014-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802183516/https://pressfreedomfoundation.org/blog/2013/10/freedom-press-foundation-launches-securedrop|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://pressfreedomfoundation.org/blog/2014/03/renowned-technologists-journalists-join-freedom-press-foundation-technical-advisory|title=Renowned Technologists, Journalists Join Freedom of the Press Foundation Technical Advisory Board|publisher=pressfreedomfoundation.org|date=2014-03-12|accessdate=2015-11-29|language=en|archive-date=2014-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140323062015/https://pressfreedomfoundation.org/blog/2014/03/renowned-technologists-journalists-join-freedom-press-foundation-technical-advisory|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 獲獎 ==
鮑爾森於2008年獲J-Lab頒發科耐特-巴頓新聞創新大獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.j-lab.org/projects/knight-batten-awards-for-innovations-in-journalism/2008|title=Knight-Batten 2008 Winners » Projects » J-Lab|publisher=J-lab.org|date=2011-07-20|accessdate=2015-11-28|language=en|archive-date=2015-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215092517/http://www.j-lab.org/projects/knight-batten-awards-for-innovations-in-journalism/2008|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2009年獲《產銷快訊》雜誌選為該雜誌的數位名人堂成員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.minonline.com/best_of_web/Digital-Hall-of-Fame-Kevin-Poulson-Senior-Editor-Wired-com_10282.html|title=Digital Hall of Fame: Kevin Poulsen, Senior Editor, Wired.com|publisher=MinOnline|date=2011-12-08|accessdate=2015-12-28|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129180100/http://www.minonline.com/best_of_web/Digital-Hall-of-Fame-Kevin-Poulson-Senior-Editor-Wired-com_10282.html|archivedate=2012-01-29}}</ref>。2010年則獲得{{link-en|SANS研究所|SANS Institute}}的最佳資安記者獎<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sans.org/top-journalists/2010|title=2010 Top Cyber Security Journalist Award Winners|publisher=SANS|date=2009-07-24|accessdate=2015-11-28|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195000/https://www.sans.org/top-journalists/2010|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而鮑爾森與{{link-en|賴恩·辛格爾|Ryan Singel|-{zh-hant:賴恩·辛格爾;zh-hans:瑞恩·辛格}-}}共筆的部落格Threat Level於2010年獲《產銷快訊》雜誌的最佳部落格獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.minonline.com/awards/bestofweb10/|title=min's 2010 Best of the Web Awards|publisher=MinOnline|date=|accessdate=2015-12-28|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206130837/http://www.minonline.com/awards/bestofweb10/|archivedate=2012-02-06}}</ref>，2011年獲{{link-en|國際數位藝術與科學學院|International Academy of Digital Arts and Sciences}}[[威比奖|威比奖]]的法律類獎，同時也獲該類的人民之聲獎（{{lang|en|People's Voice award}}）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://webbyawards.com/winners/2011/web/general-website/law/threat-level/|title=2011 People's Voice / Webby Award Winner - THREAT LEVEL|publisher=Webbyawards.com|date=2011-10-28|accessdate=2015-11-28|language=en}}</ref>

== 著作 ==
凱文·鮑爾森於2011年撰寫了一本關於駭客的英文小說《{{link-en|掘金黑客：马克斯·维京：地下网络犯罪之王|Kingpin (book)}}》，該小說後來被翻譯成[[波蘭文|波蘭文]]、[[簡體中文|簡體中文]]、[[日文|日文]]、[[義大利文|義大利文]]、[[葡萄牙文|葡萄牙文]]等語言，在多國發行。<ref>{{cite book|author=凱文·鮑爾森|title=Kingpin: How One Hacker Took Over the Billion-Dollar Cybercrime Underground| series =| year = 2011| publisher = Crown| isbn= 978-0-307-58868-5|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=凱文·鮑爾森|title=Kingpin: The True Story Of Max Butler, The Master Hacker Who Ran A Billion Dollar Cyber Crime Network| series =| year = 2011| publisher = Hachette (Australia)| isbn= 978-0-7336-2771-2|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=凱文·鮑爾森|title=Haker: Prawdziwa historia szefa cybermafii| series =| year = 2011| publisher = Znak (Poland) | isbn=978-83-240-1659-4|language=pl}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=凱文·鮑爾森|title=掘金黑客:马克斯•维京:地下网络犯罪之王| series =| year = 2012| publisher = Electronic Industry Press" (China) | isbn= 978-71-2118-488-8|language=zh-hans}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=凱文·鮑爾森|title=アイスマン| series =| year = 2012| publisher = Shodensha (Japan) | isbn=978-43-9665-048-3|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=凱文·鮑爾森|title=Kingpin: La vera storia della rapina digitale più incredibile del secolo| series =| year = 2013| publisher = Hoepli (Italy) | isbn=978-88-203-5229-5|language=it}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=凱文·鮑爾森|title=Chefão: Como um Hacker Se Apoderou do Submundo Bilionário do Crime Cibernético| series =| year = 2014| publisher = Alta Books (Brazil) | isbn=978-85-7608-772-4|language=pt}}</ref>

